title: E285 DJ Scheme Shares Final Moments With Juice WRLD & XXXTENTACION
itunes:title: DJ Scheme Shares Final Moments With Juice WRLD & XXXTENTACION
description:
Coveted music producer, DJ Scheme, joins the boys to discuss untold stories of Juice WRLD & XXXTENTACION, their final words to him before passing away, how he’s coped with losing multiple best friends, astonishing tour moments with Juice WRLD, X’s passion for fighting & personal growth, and much more…
